<link=\"CRABSPECIES\">Pokeshell</link> molt is an excellent source of <link=\"LIME\">Lime</link> but much care must be taken with domesticating this species as it can get aggressive around its eggs.\n\nHarvesting <link=\"SEALETTUCE\">Waterweed</link> provides <link=\"LETTUCE\">Lettuce</link> for many higher-tier <link=\"FOOD\">foods</link>.\n\nAny <link=\"WATER\">Water</link> will need to be filtered through a <link=\"DESALINATOR\">Desalinator</link> to remove the <link=\"SALT\">Salt</link> in order to make it useful for my Duplicants. Luckily <link=\"SALT\">Table Salt</link> can be produced using a <link=\"ROCKCRUSHER\">Rock Crusher</link> which, when combined with a <link=\"DININGTABLE\">Mess Table</link>, gives my Duplicants a <link=\"MORALE\">Morale</link> boost.